自定义的转换器：

``` Java
public class CustomerFastJsonHttpMessageConverter extends FastJsonHttpMessageConverter
{
    public CustomerFastJsonHttpMessageConverter()
    {
        super();
        SerializeConfig.getGlobalInstance().addFilter(Field_options.class, new PropertyPreFilter()
        {

            @Override
            public boolean apply(JSONSerializer serializer, Object obj, String name)
            {
                if (null == obj)
                {
                    return true;
                }

                //只有条形码和二维码题目的时候才会返回这两个字段
                if ("execute_rule".equalsIgnoreCase(name) || "execute_img".equalsIgnoreCase(name))
                {
                    Field_options field = (Field_options)obj;
                    if ("barcode".equalsIgnoreCase(field.getField_type())
                            || "qrcode".equalsIgnoreCase(field.getField_type()))
                    {
                        return true;
                    }
                    return false;
                }

                return true;
            }
        });
    }
}
```

